content.text:
I'm ready to help you with your project! This appears to be a Python-based cargo/email processing system with several directories and scripts.

From the git status, I can see you have:
- Various Python scripts for cargo report generation and email extraction
- Several directories with Chinese names (appears to be cargo/vending related projects)
- Some test directories (test_1 through test_4, test_9)
- Environment file (.env)

What would you like me to help you with? I can:
- Help organize or commit these files
- Review or modify the Python scripts
- Set up the project structure
- Run tests or analyses
- Or any other task you have in mind

Just let me know what you'd like to work on!
